org.gridgain.grid.cache.query
Interface GridCacheQueryMetrics

public interface GridCacheQueryMetrics

Cache query metrics used to obtain statistics on query. You can get query metrics via GridCache.queryMetrics() method which will provide metrics for all queries executed on cache.

Note that in addition to query metrics, you can also enable query tracing by setting "org.gridgain.cache.queries" logging category to DEBUG level.
